name: Kachua Shet Bot
description: Kachua Shet is the only Discord bot you'll ever need. It has powerfull latest features which can manage discord server. It contains latest discord features like buttons, forms, menu, etc
feature1: Economy, It can play different kind of games and earn in-game currency, items, etc.
feature2: Moderation, It has many moderation command with latest discord fetures like timeout.
feature3: WantedPoster, It can make a wanted poster of a user with their avatar, etc.
feature4: Ticket, It is very easy to pull the ticket and close it. It has buttons to make more easy to use.
